metadata.name: Lara's Valentine's Day
metadata.description:
"Do you want some chocolate?"

Your classmate Lara wasn't very close. She suddenly calls you and gives you chocolate. Actually, she is demon. she disguised herself as a human being to seduce you into hell. 

"What are you doing? Hurry up and get this."

If you eat chocolate, you'll end up in hell... but she's too beautiful to say no. What should I do?!


(Every bidder will receive a gif nft at the end of this piece's auction.)
